                <div class="banner-stat__text">
                  <h1 style="font-size:24px;line-height:24px;font-weight:900;">How does SmileDirectClub’s bright on premium teeth whitening work?</h1>
                  <p>SmileDirectClub’s teeth whitening kits contain everything to whiten your teeth and achieve your brightest bright. Our bright on&trade; whitening gel gets teeth up to 9 shades whiter in just 1 week*, and contains the same enamel-safe whitening agent used by dentists – for less than half the cost.</p>
