                  <p>Plus, the no-mess brush applicator keeps gel off your hands and on your teeth, where it starts working right away. The patented 20-LED accelerator light accelerates our bright boost formula, so you can see your brightest bright even faster. It’s powered by your smartphone (iPhone or Android), so it’s hands-free and portable – that means you can brighten wherever, whenever.</p>
